{"tid":395854,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果無珍惜 點解會傷心","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T07:34:34.000Z","uid":142226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08dc45d4b0899be29e2e39af93b92cbacf466898","tid":395854,"uid":142226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"曾經有個一齊左四年幾既男朋友<br />\n當時既我好愛好愛佢<br />\n但係佢一次又一次講大話搵其他女<br />\n有幾多次我都原諒幾多次<br />\n天真到以為佢總有一日會改<br />\n其實本性難移 就算俾幾多時間你都係一樣<br />\n我累了放手了 你其實都無珍惜過我<br />\n有咩資格講你受傷<br />\n請你放過我亦都放過你自己<br />\n傷害太多 唔想一一提起<br />\n利申:藍絲"},{"pid":"623248e6bd63855c6117e5e14d998ec50ffb3f6f","tid":395854,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b3a2f07518f1ec8b358847ae41ee260d38e91c","tid":395854,"uid":142226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n非gay"}]}